snippet.title: Togges - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
This is a Trailer!

Togges is a Collect-A-Thon 3D Platformer about adorable little cubes in an adventure to dominate the universe and save the galaxy!

This trailer was part of the "Hubworld Direct" - A collective between indie developers creating amazing 3D Platformers:

https://youtu.be/Oet4SHg3jB8

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
